--------------------
Dibblr and Last.fm integration
Set audio/video files as ringtone + media converter
BT file exchange (GameKit or BTstack)
Wi-Fi ad-hoc network file sharing - SEMI-DONE
iPad support
Grouping by genres in MyPod
Google (Docs and Plus) integration
DMG file support
Video and more audio metadata support via TagLib
Dropbox and local thumbnails
Use MPOAuthiOS, CarbonateTwitter and CarbonateJSON instead of MGTwitterEngine, SA_OAuthtTwitterEngine, TouchJSON and OAuthConsumer

